<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200808/928f99f48d384f758c9980054364fc3f.png" /></p>
<p><span>有网友表示</span></p>
<p><span><strong>“童言无忌，广告有忌”</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>“希望能加强公共场合广告审核”</strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200808/86085433042b4369acc95c727ef7cc4f.png" /></p>
